com.fujitsu.xml.xlink.dataset
Interface XLinkDeclarationHashtable

public interface XLinkDeclarationHashtable

Interface that provides a link declaration information list table.
A link declaration information list is mapped with a DOM document used as a key.

Method Summary

Method Detail

get

public XLinkDeclarationList get(Document owner)
The link declaration information list mapped with the document is obtained.
Parameters:
owner - DOM document used as a key.
Returns:
The link declaration information list mapped with the key is returned. If no link declaration information list is mapped with the key or the key is null, null is returned.

size

public int size()
The number of registered documents is obtained.
Returns:
The number of registered documents is returned.

containsKey

public boolean containsKey(Document owner)
Whether a link declaration information list is registered with a specified document is judged.
Parameters:
owner - Document to be judged.
Returns:
The judgment result is returned.
true is returned when a link declaration information list is registered with owner; otherwise, false is returned.

keys

public java.util.Enumeration keys()
A list of registered documents is obtained.
Documents can be fetched sequentially by using the Enumeration method.
Returns:
The list of registered documents is returned.

elements

public java.util.Enumeration elements()
A list of registered link declaration information lists is obtained.
Link declaration information lists can be fetched sequentially by using the Enumeration method.
Returns:
The list of registered link declaration information lists is returned.
